                 SimulatedTorqueData, SimulatedVelocityData,
                 AxisSysMLModel, MotorSimulinkModel, GearboxSimulinkModel, FrictionSimulinkModel,
                 FrictionIdentificationService, DataComparisonService, DashboardVisualizationService,
